<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>十月怀胎计划｜孕育新的自己</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f7f7fb;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --text: #1f2430;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --line: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #7c3aed;
      --accent-soft: #ede9fe;
      --good: #16a34a;
      --warn: #d97706;
      --bad: #dc2626;
      --shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.06);
      --radius: 16px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC",
        "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "Noto Sans CJK SC", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #faf5ff 0%, #eef2ff 100%);
      border: 1px solid #ede9fe;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 22px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 26px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .identity {
      margin-top: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      border: 1px dashed #c4b5fd;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }

    .tab-btn {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .tab-btn.active {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .grid-2, .grid-3 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .card h2, .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .card h2 { font-size: 20px; }
    .card h3 { font-size: 16px; }

    .muted { color: var(--muted); }

    .row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 140px;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .row label {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    input[type="number"],
    input[type="date"],
    textarea,
    select {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font: inherit;
      background: #fff;
    }

    textarea {
      min-height: 90px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    button {
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 700;
      font: inherit;
    }

    .primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: white;
    }

    .secondary {
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .danger {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: #991b1b;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: #5b21b6;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-right: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .kpi {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .kpi .value {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .kpi .label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .progress-wrap {
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .progress-label {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .progress {
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #eef2f7;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .progress > span {
      display: block;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #6366f1 100%);
      width: 0%;
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }

    .month-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .month-item {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .month-item.active {
      border-color: #c4b5fd;
      background: #faf5ff;
    }

    .month-title {
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    ul {
      margin: 8px 0 0 18px;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .small {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .table-like {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .entry {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .entry-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .status-good { color: var(--good); }
    .status-warn { color: var(--warn); }
    .status-bad { color: var(--bad); }

    .hidden { display: none; }

    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .inline {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .checkbox-line {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--line);
      margin: 12px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>十月怀胎计划｜孕育一个全新的自己</h1>
      <p>
        不是逼自己一夜重生，而是稳定供养，按月发育。你在经历一场十月怀胎，只不过你孕育的是新的自己。
      </p>
      <div class="identity" id="identityStatement">
        我是一个在压力、内耗和现实责任都存在的情况下，仍然能稳定保护长期目标、持续行动、并照顾身体的人。
      </div>
      <div class="actions">
        <button class="secondary" id="editIdentityBtn">修改身份句子</button>
        <button class="secondary" id="exportBtn">导出数据（JSON）</button>
        <button class="secondary" id="importBtn">导入数据（JSON）</button>
        <input id="importFile" type="file" accept=".json" class="hidden" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="tabs">
      <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="overview">孕程总览</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="daily">今日记录</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="weekly">周复盘</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="months">十个月计划</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="history">记录历史</button>
    </div>

    <!-- OVERVIEW -->
    <section id="tab-overview" class="tab-panel">
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>当前阶段总览</h2>
          <div class="inline" style="margin-bottom:8px;">
            <span class="pill" id="currentMonthPill">第1个月｜着床期</span>
            <span class="pill" id="currentWeekPill">第1周</span>
            <span class="pill" id="dayCountPill">第1天</span>
          </div>
          <p class="muted small" id="currentThemeText"></p>

          <div class="divider"></div>

          <h3>本月目标完成度</h3>
          <div class="progress-wrap">
            <div class="progress-label"><span>人生推进任务天数</span><span id="progressTaskLabel">0 / 20</span></div>
            <div class="progress"><span id="progressTaskBar"></span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="progress-wrap">
            <div class="progress-label"><span>运动次数</span><span id="progressExerciseLabel">0 / 16</span></div>
            <div class="progress"><span id="progressExerciseBar"></span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="progress-wrap">
            <div class="progress-label"><span>记录完成天数</span><span id="progressLogLabel">0 / 20</span></div>
            <div class="progress"><span id="progressLogBar"></span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="divider"></div>

          <h3>本月提醒</h3>
          <ul id="currentMonthWarnings"></ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>最近7天产检数据</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top: 8px;">
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="value" id="kpiResearch">0h</div>
              <div class="label">科研深度工作</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="value" id="kpiExercise">0次</div>
              <div class="label">运动天数</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="value" id="kpiScreen">0h</div>
              <div class="label">屏幕逃避</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="value" id="kpiSleep">0h</div>
              <div class="label">平均睡眠</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="value" id="kpiEnergy">0</div>
              <div class="label">平均精力评分</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
              <div class="value" id="kpiHighPressure">0%</div>
              <div class="label">高压日执行率</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="divider"></div>

          <h3>系统判读</h3>
          <p id="systemAssessment" class="small muted">
            先记录数据，你的趋势会慢慢浮出来。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- DAILY -->
    <section id="tab-daily" class="tab-panel hidden">
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>今日营养输入</h2>
          <p class="muted small">输入低成本，持续最重要。今天做到最低营养配方，就算你在养新自己。</p>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="entryDate">日期</label>
            <input type="date" id="entryDate" />
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="researchMinutes">科研深度工作（分钟）</label>
            <input type="number" id="researchMinutes" min="0" step="5" placeholder="例如 25" />
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="workMinutes">工作/兼职（分钟）</label>
            <input type="number" id="workMinutes" min="0" step="5" placeholder="例如 360" />
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="exerciseMinutes">运动（分钟）</label>
            <input type="number" id="exerciseMinutes" min="0" step="5" placeholder="例如 20" />
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="screenMinutes">屏幕逃避（分钟）</label>
            <input type="number" id="screenMinutes" min="0" step="5" placeholder="例如 45" />
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="sleepHours">睡眠（小时）</label>
            <input type="number" id="sleepHours" min="0" max="24" step="0.5" placeholder="例如 7" />
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="recoveryMinutes">恢复行为（分钟）</label>
            <input type="number" id="recoveryMinutes" min="0" step="5" placeholder="散步 / 拉伸 / 安静吃饭 / 陪猫" />
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="energyScore">精力评分（1到10）</label>
            <input type="number" id="energyScore" min="1" max="10" step="1" placeholder="例如 6" />
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="messageHijacks">被消息劫持次数</label>
            <input type="number" id="messageHijacks" min="0" step="1" placeholder="例如 3" />
          </div>

          <div class="checkbox-line">
            <input type="checkbox" id="didKeyTask" />
            <label for="didKeyTask">今天完成了“人生推进任务”最小块（25分钟或以上）</label>
          </div>

          <div class="checkbox-line">
            <input type="checkbox" id="highPressureDay" />
            <label for="highPressureDay">今天是高压日（工作多 / 家里乱 / 猫咪状态差 / 情绪很重）</label>
          </div>

          <div class="checkbox-line">
            <input type="checkbox" id="didMinActionInAnxiety" />
            <label for="didMinActionInAnxiety">焦虑时仍完成了最小动作</label>
          </div>

          <div class="row" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
            <label for="dailyNote">今日胎动（备注）</label>
            <textarea id="dailyNote" placeholder="今天最明显的进步 / 被劫持原因 / 一个真实观察"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <button class="primary" id="saveEntryBtn">保存今日记录</button>
            <button class="secondary" id="loadTodayBtn">读取当天记录</button>
            <button class="danger" id="deleteTodayBtn">删除当天记录</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>今日产检提示</h2>
          <div id="dailyHints" class="table-like">
            <div class="entry">
              <div class="entry-header">
                <span>最低营养配方</span>
                <span class="status-warn">未检测</span>
              </div>
              <div class="small muted">25分钟关键任务 + 15分钟运动 + 3分钟记录 + 1个恢复动作 + 消息窗口化</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="divider"></div>

          <h3>今日作战提醒</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>情绪可以坐副驾，但不能抢方向盘</li>
            <li>计划时间封顶15分钟，然后开始25分钟</li>
            <li>先做人生推进任务，再做别人要的任务</li>
            <li>波动日不是失败日，只是恢复日</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WEEKLY -->
    <section id="tab-weekly" class="tab-panel hidden">
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>周复盘｜产检门诊</h2>
          <p class="muted small">每周只改三件事，别贪多。系统升级靠微调，不靠暴力。</p>

          <div class="row">
            <label for="weeklyDate">复盘日期</label>
            <input type="date" id="weeklyDate" />
          </div>

          <div class="row" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
            <label for="weeklyWins">本周完成了什么（证据）</label>
            <textarea id="weeklyWins" placeholder="例如：5天做了科研最小块，运动4次，交了scoping review给导师"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="row" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
            <label for="weeklyHijacks">本周被什么劫持（真实一点）</label>
            <textarea id="weeklyHijacks" placeholder="例如：工作消息、临时备课、情绪爆炸、报复性熬夜"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="row" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
            <label for="weeklyWorks">哪些动作真的有效（保留）</label>
            <textarea id="weeklyWorks" placeholder="例如：起床后先做25分钟科研、关通知、晚间15分钟走路"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="row" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
            <label for="weeklyAdjustments">下周只改三件事（医嘱）</label>
            <textarea id="weeklyAdjustments" placeholder="1. 保留一个动作 2. 删掉一个动作 3. 升级一个动作"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <button class="primary" id="saveWeeklyBtn">保存周复盘</button>
            <button class="secondary" id="loadWeeklyBtn">读取该日复盘</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>本周快速统计</h2>
          <div id="weeklySnapshot" class="table-like"></div>

          <div class="divider"></div>

          <h3>周复盘历史</h3>
          <div id="weeklyHistory" class="table-like">
            <div class="entry small muted">还没有周复盘记录</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MONTHS -->
    <section id="tab-months" class="tab-panel hidden">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>十个月发育计划</h2>
        <p class="muted small">
          不是每天证明自己多狠，而是稳定供养，按月发育，按阶段成形。每个月都有发育重点、监测指标和达成标准。
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
          <button class="secondary" id="prevMonthBtn">上一月</button>
          <button class="secondary" id="nextMonthBtn">下一月</button>
        </div>

        <div id="monthsContainer" class="month-list" style="margin-top:12px;"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- HISTORY -->
    <section id="tab-history" class="tab-panel hidden">
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>每日记录历史</h2>
          <div id="historyList" class="table-like">
            <div class="entry small muted">还没有每日记录</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>数据说明</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>所有数据默认保存在你的浏览器本地（localStorage）</li>
            <li>换设备或清除浏览器缓存会丢失数据，所以建议定期导出 JSON</li>
            <li>你可以后续升级成 Firebase 或 Supabase 做云同步</li>
            <li>先跑起来最重要，不要被“技术洁癖”拖住</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <h3>最小营养配方提醒</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>25分钟关键任务</li>
            <li>15分钟运动</li>
            <li>3分钟记录</li>
            <li>1个恢复动作</li>
            <li>消息窗口化</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <p class="footer-note">
      这不是打卡羞辱器，这是你的孕程照护系统。允许波动，持续供养。
    </p>
  </div>

  <script>
